# Cypress

Cypress is a next generation front end testing tool built for the modern web. Fast, easy and reliable testing for anything that runs in a browser.

## Key Features

- **Time-travel debugging** to see exactly what happened at each step
- **Real browser testing** with Chrome, Edge, and Firefox
- **Automatic waiting** eliminates flaky tests
- **Network stubbing** to control API responses
- **Screenshots and videos** of test runs automatically
- **Live browser reloading** during test development
- **Cross-browser testing** with consistent behavior

## Use Cases

- End-to-end testing of web applications
- Integration testing
- Unit testing of front-end components
- API testing
- Visual regression testing

## Get Started with Cypress

Test your app like a user would. Visit [cypress.io](https://www.cypress.io) to install Cypress and start writing reliable tests that actually work.